\/now-hiring-web1-600x400.jpg\" alt=\"now-hiring-web\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.gottwalsbooks.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/now-hiring-web1-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.gottwalsbooks.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/now-hiring-web1-234x156.jpg 234w, https:\/\/www.gottwalsbooks.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/now-hiring-web1.jpg 900w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2>Celebrating Black History Month at Gottwals<\/h2>\n<p>We have shelves of great fiction and nonfiction titles from African American authors!<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-5187\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/black-history-webready-600x338.jpg\" alt=\"black-history-webready\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.gottwalsbooks.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/black-history-webready-600x338.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.gottwalsbooks.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/black-history-webready-277x156.jpg 277w, https:\/\/www.gottwalsbooks.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/black-history-webready.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-5188\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/black-history-2-webready-338x600.jpg\" alt=\"black-history-2-webready\" width=\"338\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.gottwalsbooks.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/black-history-2-webready-338x600.jpg 338w, https:\/\/www.gottwalsbooks.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/black-history-2-webready-88x156.jpg 88w, https:\/\/www.gottwalsbooks.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/black-history-2-webready.jpg 675w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 338px) 100vw, 338px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2>Toy of the Week<\/h2>\n<p><strong>Fish Colors Mix &#8216;n Match Peg Puzzle &#8211; 10 pieces: $7.97<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>This wooden peg puzzle, featuring 10 colorful fish, includes ten interchangeable pieces, allowing c